        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/coastaltown/_scene_copperhead.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 69e1755e-2d5c-4106-a67a-1fb37e4f9ab0).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47. Welcome to the beautiful town of Sapienza, Italy.\r\rWhile Dino Bosco is shooting for his new film, Enrico Nucci, a crimelord famous for arms trafficking throughout Europe has been spotted.\r\rInside sources tell us that he is a bit salty at the moment, as he was recently removed from his special effects manager role on the film set. A double agent working with both the ICA and Mr. Nucci&#39;s crew has said that he apparently plans on killing the new manager later tonight with an explosion.\r\rIn order to prevent this hit, you need to perform a hit yourself, 47. Enrico can be found at a stand displaying some Dino Bosco merchandise in the corner of town. In order to make it even more amusing, disguise yourself as an SFX Crew member. This will also help with your additional objective.\r\rTo prevent the use in any attack against the incumbent manager, retrieve the high octane fuel from within the Ceramics Shop after eliminating Mr. Nucci.\r\rGood luck.",
